msg: Pass the temp text base path down the call stack only if there is a temp
text base file, otherwise pass NULL.  A follow-up to r927056.

(install_committed_file): Don't check whether the new base text file
exists: if the caller provides a file name, that means it exists.
(run_postcommit, svn_wc__wq_add_postcommit): Support the temp text base
